41
00:02:22,212 --> 00:02:25,748
Emergency room?

42
00:02:31,653 --> 00:02:35,524
Why isn't he picking up the phone?

43
00:02:39,995 --> 00:02:41,348
Excuse me,

44
00:02:41,348 --> 00:02:42,954
