146
00:09:36,349 --> 00:09:38,885
Something bad can happen, Mom!

147
00:09:42,808 --> 00:09:44,525
Death is the worst thing that can happen.

148
00:09:44,525 --> 00:09:46,078
Leave me alone.

149
00:09:51,789 --> 00:09:55,080
