198
00:13:02,753 --> 00:13:05,002
However...

199
00:13:05,002 --> 00:13:06,982
What do you mean?

200
00:13:06,982 --> 00:13:09,601
Since trauma to the brain was severe,

201
00:13:09,601 --> 00:13:14,045
