241
00:16:43,304 --> 00:16:46,378
I am too ashamed to see you.

242
00:16:46,378 --> 00:16:49,499
Nothing bad will happen.

243
00:16:50,320 --> 00:16:53,996
After he sleeps well tonight,

244
00:16:54,545 --> 00:16:59,230
